<h1>The Worlds of Pele's Playground</h1>

<p>Welcome to Pele's Playground! Here you'll find easy links to our worlds
and the stories in them. Some worlds have a large number of stories
waiting to be released; others have only one or two.</p>

<p>Some of these stories are complete; others are essentially complete,
but need editing (a very time-consuming task). We've recently changed
how we do our writing, dropping the time needed to prepare a rough
draft from an hour for 1,500 words to an hour for approximately 12,000
words; expect to see a lot of the newer stuff before the older stuff
makes it out. Luckily, however, none of our stories are in any
particular chronological order, and none depend on the others to any
great degree.</p>

<p>Note that most of these links won't work yet; only stories which we have released at least one chapter have more than a nominal webpage. </p>

<p>Also, <strong>we have forums!</strong> Go <strong><a href="http://playground.pele.cx/forums">here</a></strong> to discuss the stories!</a></p>

